  "response": "Whether it is okay to spend the night with your fianc\u00e9 largely depends on your personal beliefs, religious convictions, and cultural traditions. Different religious teachings have varied views on pre-marital relationships. For instance, some Christian denominations may advise against pre-marital cohabitation based on biblical principles. Other religions and cultures may have different positions on this matter.\n\nIt is important to consider your own values, your understanding of your faith, and what feels right for you and your partner. Consulting with a trusted religious leader, counselor, or mentor might also offer guidance tailored to your specific beliefs and circumstances. Ultimately, the decision should be made thoughtfully and respectfully between you and your fianc\u00e9.",
